{
  "name": "LAB",
  "width": 14,
  "height": 11,
  "tilesize": 16,
  "tiles": "WWWWWWWWWWWWWW\nW..b........bW\nW..b........bW\nW............W\nW............W\nW............W\nW............W\nW.SSS........W\nW............W\nW............W\nWWWWWdWWWWWWWW",
  "_layout": "14x11. Bookshelves cap NW/NE corners (b). Three pedestals SSS at (2-4, 7) — the starter pedestals (visual; the actual choice is via Larch's interact). Larch NPC at (3,4). KAMON theft step-on at (5,9), requiresFlag=player_has_starter. South door (d) → HEARTHWICK.",
  "tileset": {
    "W": { "color": "#5a4a2a", "solid": true, "label": "wall" },
    ".": { "color": "#b9bcc9", "solid": false, "label": "floor" },
    "b": { "color": "#4a3c1f", "solid": true, "label": "bookshelf" },
    "S": { "color": "#7a3e0c", "solid": true, "label": "pedestal" },
    "d": { "color": "#daa520", "solid": false, "label": "door" }
  },
  "objects": [
    {
      "type": "warp",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 10,
      "target": "HEARTHWICK:fromLab"
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 1,
      "y": 7,
      "lines": [
        "Pedestal: KINDRAKE",
        "Sturdy. Slow.",
        "Take a hit, dish one back."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 2,
      "y": 7,
      "lines": [
        "Pedestal: GRUBLEAF",
        "Quick. Light.",
        "Reads beat raw force."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sign",
      "x": 3,
      "y": 7,
      "lines": [
        "Pedestal: SILTSKIP",
        "Patient. Heavy.",
        "Turns aggression back on itself."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "x": 3,
      "y": 4,
      "color": "#c5cfe2",
      "interact": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LARCH: You're the last one who",
            "answered. Years ago there'd be",
            "a line of children at my door",
            "on a morning like this.",
            "Now... just you.",
            "",
            "LARCH: I'm not giving you a",
            "partner — I'm asking you to",
            "carry something.",
            "The way of the trainer,",
            "before it's gone for good.",
            "",
            "These three have been waiting.",
            "Not for the strongest hand.",
            "For the right one.",
            "LARCH: Strength fades.",
            "The bond is what lasts.",
            "Prove me right."
          ]
        },
        { "kind": "show-starter-pick" }
      ],
      "interactAfterFlag": [
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "kamon_took_starter",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "LARCH: Head south,",
                "through Route 31.",
                "A parcel waits in the next town.",
                "Go on."
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "blockedUntilFlag": "player_has_starter"
    },
    {
      "type": "script",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 9,
      "trigger": "step-on",
      "requiresFlag": "player_has_starter",
      "flag": "kamon_theft_fired",
      "once": true,
      "commands": [
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "The lab door slams open.",
            "KAMON marches in.",
            "",
            "KAMON: Sentiment.",
            "He hands the future to a kid",
            "because of 'bonds.'",
            "",
            "KAMON: Strength is the only",
            "thing that's ever lasted.",
            "Not feelings.",
            "Not some old man's hope."
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_kindrake",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "KAMON grabs the SILTSKIP.",
                "",
                "KAMON: I'll prove it with the",
                "one that beats yours.",
                "Don't take it personally —",
                "I intend to be right.",
                "",
                "(The SILTSKIP hesitates",
                "in his arms.)",
                "KAMON: ...It'll learn."
              ]
            },
            { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "kamon_took_siltskip" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_grubleaf",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "KAMON grabs the KINDRAKE.",
                "",
                "KAMON: I'll prove it with the",
                "one that beats yours.",
                "Don't take it personally —",
                "I intend to be right.",
                "",
                "(The KINDRAKE hesitates",
                "in his arms.)",
                "KAMON: ...It'll learn."
              ]
            },
            { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "kamon_took_kindrake" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_siltskip",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "KAMON grabs the GRUBLEAF.",
                "",
                "KAMON: I'll prove it with the",
                "one that beats yours.",
                "Don't take it personally —",
                "I intend to be right.",
                "",
                "(The GRUBLEAF hesitates",
                "in his arms.)",
                "KAMON: ...It'll learn."
              ]
            },
            { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "kamon_took_grubleaf" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "KAMON storms out.",
            "",
            "LARCH watches the door",
            "for a long moment.",
            "",
            "LARCH: ...He's wrong, you know."
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_kindrake",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "LARCH: That FLAME-type of yours —",
                "give it time.",
                "Fire trusts slowly."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_grubleaf",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "LARCH: That NATURE-type of yours —",
                "give it time.",
                "Roots grow patient."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "if-flag",
          "flag": "starter_siltskip",
          "commands": [
            {
              "kind": "dialog",
              "lines": [
                "LARCH: That AQUA-type of yours —",
                "give it time.",
                "Water remembers."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LARCH: He didn't wait for the",
            "most important part.",
            "",
            "LARCH: There are two ways to earn",
            "a creature's place beside you.",
            "",
            "LARCH: You can out-read it in a",
            "fight — force an opening in its",
            "guard, and in that opening, catch.",
            "",
            "LARCH: Or you can spare it, and",
            "let it choose you. But that path",
            "comes later, once you've earned",
            "the standing out there.",
            "Most only ever learn the first."
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LARCH lifts a contained FLITPECK",
            "onto the bench. Watch closely.",
            "",
            "LARCH: It's gathering to lunge —",
            "see how it coils?",
            "Brace, and force the opening.",
            "",
            "(The FLITPECK strikes; LARCH's",
            "mon braces — the bird overcommits",
            "and is left exposed.)",
            "",
            "LARCH: There — it's open.",
            "NOW the throw.",
            "",
            "(A band arcs out. A flash.)",
            "LARCH: Gotcha. That's a read-catch.",
            "Read, open, throw. That's all of it."
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LARCH presses a handful of",
            "BANDS into your pack.",
            "",
            "LARCH: Five to start. Spend them",
            "on the opening you make —",
            "never on a guard you haven't broken."
          ]
        },
        { "kind": "give-item", "itemId": "BALL", "qty": 5 },
        { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "catch_lesson_done" },
        {
          "kind": "dialog",
          "lines": [
            "LARCH: Head south,",
            "through Route 31.",
            "Try it on a real one out there.",
            "A parcel waits in the next town.",
            "Go on."
          ]
        },
        { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "kamon_took_starter" },
        { "kind": "set-flag", "flag": "pushed_south" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "spawns": {
    "default": { "x": 5, "y": 8, "facing": "up" },
    "fromHearthwick": { "x": 5, "y": 9, "facing": "up" },
    "fromRoute": { "x": 5, "y": 9, "facing": "up" }
  }
}
